snippet.title: Graveyard Keeper: Breaking Dead Trailer
snippet.description: Introducing the first DLC for Graveyard Keeper, and it's free for all Steam users (part of main game now)! Use the Resurrection table to build an army of the undead.. to do your graveyard chores ;) https://store.steampowered.com/app/599140/Graveyard_Keeper/
